		<h3>Open Season</h3>
				<dl>
					<dt>Summer Season:</dt>
					<dd>May 15 - October 15<br />9:00 A.M. to 6:30 P.M.</dd>
					<dt>Winter Season:</dt>
					<dd>October 16 to May 14<br />9:00 A.M. to 3:00 P.M.</dd>
				</dl>
